The 41st Annual Hunger Walk Run is less than TWO weeks away! Join thousands of your neighbors at the Home Depot Backyard or virtually on March 9th to help support local food pantries and meal programs across Atlanta. Let's cross the finish line together for a better community!

Register today: https://www.hungerwalkrun.org

Thank you to our sponsors for supporting this event: Georgia Power, Inspire Brands, IHG Hotels & Resorts, The Coca-Cola Company, The Home Depot Backyard, Beazer Homes, Northside Hospital, and Tokio Marine America

Register today and be a part of the movement to end hunger.
